ADDITIONAL NOTICE — OPERATIONAL USE

SENTRY / IgnisLink is an assistive surveillance and triage layer. It is NOT a
substitute for 911, official evacuation orders, or human dispatch judgement.
The Public Awareness Map is situational data only — for evacuation orders,
follow your local Authority Having Jurisdiction (Cal Fire, county OES, or
municipal fire department). The fire-spread model's predicted contours are
probabilistic and have documented limitations; see docs/ml-model-card.md
before relying on them in any operational context.
